rban landscapes, religious worldview, and the evolution of social relations at all levels of society during the twilight of the late-Roman state. This is the first full translation of this masterwork into English.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 7aRELIGION / Ancient.2bisacsh  abishops.  acassiodorus.  achristian.  acivil.  acriminals.  adiplomatic culture.  aeconomic structure.  aemperors.  aexegetes of antiquity.  afinancial administration.  aheirs.  ahigh ranking public official.  aintellectual heritage.  aking theoderic.  akings.  alate roman state.  alegal structure.  alegal.  aletter collection.  amediterranean.  amilitary commanders.  aostrogothic.  apolitical culture.  aprivate citizens.  areligion.  asixth century.  asocial relations.  aurban landscapes.  avariae.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig. Stud., Jewish Stud.2019 Englishz978311061074108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theology, Relig. Studies, Jewish Studies 2019z9783110606508oZDB-23-DGF08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUCA Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311065207908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311066763940uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520969735zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520969735423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780520969735.jpg  a978-3-11-061074-1  EBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig. Stud., Jewish Stud.2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-061076-5  EBOOK PACKAGE